                </div>
                <div class="column is-two-thirds">
                    <h3 class="title subsection-title dark-indigo">Compliant by design</h3>
                    <p class="muted">Demonstrating compliance is essential in any industry. With LTO Network, you can record all data entries and steps in your business processes to safeguard evidence and comply with regulations. LTO Network enables one-click compliance reporting for both internal and external communication on your business processes.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="table-container is-centered has-margin-top-40">
